      "id": "69b82ae8cc2931abf6060e9e",
      "text": "ブーメランジョーク",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773677297,
      "updated": 1773677297
    },
    {
      "id": "69b82af000000000006b9b1c",
      "text": "否定しちゃダメ！",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773677297,
      "updated": 1773677306
    },
    {
      "id": "69b82b2e00000000006b9b1f",
      "text": "（n回目の）もっとちゃんと考えなさい！",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773677359,
      "updated": 1773677454
    },
    {
      "id": "69b82b9800000000006b9b20",
      "text": "\t解説：何度も同じフレーズを使っており、考えていない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773677464,
      "updated": 1773677488
    },
    {
      "id": "69b82af900000000006b9b1d",
      "text": "（大きな声で）うるさい！",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773677306,
      "updated": 1773677533
    },
    {
      "id": "69b82bb700000000006b9b21",
